298
00:11:34.730 --> 00:11:35.570
King rises.

299
00:11:36.450 --> 00:11:38.750
Your Majesty forgets.

300
00:11:38.930 --> 00:11:41.310
It is possible the keeper of the king's

301
00:11:41.310 --> 00:11:44.270
