367
00:13:49.490 --> 00:13:51.230
You will retain me in your service.

368
00:13:51.470 --> 00:13:51.890
Service?

369
00:13:52.230 --> 00:13:54.990
You shall have a dozen lackeys to wait

370
00:13:54.990 --> 00:13:55.390
