380
00:14:08.230 --> 00:14:10.750
Exit Larizio, left second entrance.

381
00:14:11.150 --> 00:14:13.930
Well, madam, we have met at last.

382
00:14:14.190 --> 00:14:16.690
Maritana starts at his voice and listens

383
00:14:16.690 --> 00:14:17.290
