388
00:14:25.510 --> 00:14:27.690
I've been hunted by a full pack of

389
00:14:27.690 --> 00:14:31.050
Alguazils and fired at by a tolerably good

390
00:14:31.050 --> 00:14:33.470
marksman, and all for this interview.

391
00:14:33.710 --> 00:14:34.790
That voice!

392
00:14:35.270 --> 00:14:38.190
I fear to satisfy myself lest my new

393
00:14:38.190 --> 00:14:39.530
-born hopes should wither.

394
00:14:39.850 --> 00:14:40.730
