568
00:21:13.910 --> 00:21:17.210
My pride has long revolted at the deceit

569
00:21:17.210 --> 00:21:18.630
we practised on you.

570
00:21:19.330 --> 00:21:21.510
Now that you know me for what I

571
00:21:21.510 --> 00:21:23.810
am, listen to me.

572
00:21:24.310 --> 00:21:25.570
Leave me, sire.

573
00:21:25.670 --> 00:21:27.910
I implore you, leave me.

574
00:21:28.490 --> 00:21:29.210
Leave you?

575
00:21:29.630 --> 00:21:32.190
You, the only one I have ever truly

576
00:21:32.190 --> 00:21:32.690
