One step nearer and I strike.

582
00:21:47.670 --> 00:21:51.470
What, Maritana, am I so loathsome to you?

583
00:21:51.830 --> 00:21:52.530
No, sire.

584
00:21:53.150 --> 00:21:54.810
I am a wife of one who must

585
