589
00:22:02.240 --> 00:22:04.110
Don Cesar de Bazin.

590
00:22:04.690 --> 00:22:05.750
He is dead.

591
00:22:07.090 --> 00:22:09.230
Don Cesar enters left door.

592
00:22:09.390 --> 00:22:12.350
Not yet, sire, thanks to your majesty's

593
00:22:12.350 --> 00:22:13.670
