595
00:22:18.310 --> 00:22:20.070
My husband will protect me.

596
00:22:20.450 --> 00:22:21.130
Your husband?

597
00:22:21.970 --> 00:22:24.850
Don Cesar crosses right, locks both doors,

598
00:22:25.090 --> 00:22:26.570
