600
00:22:28.410 --> 00:22:30.290
Don Cesar right door.

601
00:22:30.290 --> 00:22:33.610
Locked the door, sire, that no one may

602
00:22:33.610 --> 00:22:36.430
enter, that no one may hear, that to

603
00:22:36.430 --> 00:22:38.190
