604
00:22:38.590 --> 00:22:41.970
Crosses a centre, Maritana a side.

605
00:22:42.430 --> 00:22:44.150
What will be the end of this?

606
00:22:44.630 --> 00:22:46.050
Don Cesar fiercely.

607
00:22:46.630 --> 00:22:48.750
If the persecutor of my wife had been

608
00:22:48.750 --> 00:22:51.890
a gentleman and soldier like myself, I fear

609
00:22:51.890 --> 00:22:53.950
that I should have denied him even the

610
00:22:53.950 --> 00:22:54.990
chance of an encounter.

611
00:22:55.370 --> 00:22:57.510
I think that at once I should have

612
00:22:57.510 --> 00:22:58.350
dispatched him.

613
00:22:58.350 --> 00:23:00.230
For in such a case one does not

614
00:23:00.230 --> 00:23:02.170
