625
00:23:22.530 --> 00:23:24.430
But reparation must be made.

626
00:23:24.730 --> 00:23:26.110
King with effort.

627
00:23:26.710 --> 00:23:27.750
Proceed, sir.

628
00:23:28.350 --> 00:23:31.310
Your audacity pleases me.

629
00:23:31.690 --> 00:23:34.230
Remember, Don Cesar, it is your king.

630
00:23:34.630 --> 00:23:36.030
Yes, it is my king.

631
00:23:36.730 --> 00:23:39.530
Sire, this poor, weak woman, against whom

632
00:23:39.530 --> 00:23:42.110
such power has combined, has sought the

633
00:23:42.110 --> 00:23:44.270
