634
00:23:44.750 --> 00:23:45.550
The queen?

635
00:23:45.870 --> 00:23:46.370
Yes, sire.

636
00:23:46.830 --> 00:23:48.850
I was her messenger to the palace of

637
00:23:48.850 --> 00:23:49.230
Arranges.

638
00:23:49.750 --> 00:23:52.310
Then you have seen the queen.

639
00:23:52.610 --> 00:23:53.790
