640
00:23:54.390 --> 00:23:56.570
When I arrived at the palace I was

641
00:23:56.570 --> 00:23:58.950
denied admittance, but regardless of the

642
00:23:58.950 --> 00:24:01.250
guns of the sentinels— Ah, you have been

643
