No, you forget that I am bulletproof.

645
00:24:05.290 --> 00:24:06.350
Well, well.

646
00:24:06.970 --> 00:24:08.450
I climbed the garden wall.

647
00:24:08.750 --> 00:24:10.830
Under the shadow of some trees I crept

648
00:24:10.830 --> 00:24:13.770
