652
00:24:20.470 --> 00:24:22.310
The voice of the man trembled with

653
00:24:22.310 --> 00:24:23.450
passionate emotion.

654
00:24:23.790 --> 00:24:24.870
I heard this.

655
00:24:25.770 --> 00:24:27.070
Madam, you are deceived.

656
00:24:27.210 --> 00:24:29.190
Your husband meets his mistress to-night.

657
00:24:30.250 --> 00:24:32.350
Some officers of the king should follow him

658
00:24:32.350 --> 00:24:34.950
to his secluded chateau in the forest and

659
00:24:34.950 --> 00:24:36.970
bring you proof of his infidelity.

660
00:24:37.510 --> 00:24:40.090
Who has dared to place a watch upon

661
00:24:40.090 --> 00:24:41.710
my actions?

662
00:24:42.250 --> 00:24:45.610
The man was Don José de Santarém, your

663
00:24:45.610 --> 00:24:46.650
