664
00:24:47.010 --> 00:24:49.430
The lady was the queen.

665
00:24:49.870 --> 00:24:52.670
Tis false, if it were true.

666
00:24:53.310 --> 00:24:55.510
Crosses up left towards doors.

667
00:24:56.530 --> 00:24:59.290
Don César coolly— Your Majesty forgets that

668
00:24:59.290 --> 00:25:01.250
I have locked the doors.

669
00:25:01.690 --> 00:25:02.090
Traitor!

670
00:25:02.850 --> 00:25:03.850
Comes down left.

671
00:25:04.030 --> 00:25:06.610
I told you, sire, that reparation must be

672
00:25:06.610 --> 00:25:06.970
