673
00:25:07.230 --> 00:25:08.470
Do you understand me now?

674
00:25:09.010 --> 00:25:10.770
The minister betrays his king.

675
00:25:11.090 --> 00:25:13.550
The subject would dishonour his queen.

676
00:25:13.870 --> 00:25:18.110
Don César, on your allegiance, open that

677
00:25:18.110 --> 00:25:18.690
