712
00:26:33.550 --> 00:26:35.770
No, sire, I have struck.

713
00:26:36.710 --> 00:26:39.230
Sire, your honour is preserved.

714
00:26:40.070 --> 00:26:42.450
It is now your turn to deal with

715
00:26:42.450 --> 00:26:42.910
