716
00:26:42.910 --> 00:26:45.550
Kneels and points to Maritana.

717
00:26:46.390 --> 00:26:48.270
King raises him.

718
00:26:49.090 --> 00:26:51.210
Rise, Don César.

719
00:26:52.490 --> 00:26:55.170
Drum heard in cries of, The king!

720
00:26:55.510 --> 00:26:56.190
The king!

721
00:26:56.230 --> 00:26:56.650
The king!

722
00:26:57.010 --> 00:26:59.230
The doors are burst open and nobles enter.

723
00:27:00.030 --> 00:27:01.830
Lazorillo takes back chair.

724
00:27:02.150 --> 00:27:02.530
The king!

725
00:27:02.750 --> 00:27:02.910
The king!

726
00:27:03.010 --> 00:27:03.110
The king!

727
00:27:03.930 --> 00:27:07.410
Yes, gentlemen, we have visited Don César de

728
00:27:07.410 --> 00:27:10.430
Bezan, one of your most faithful servants.

729
00:27:10.960 --> 00:27:12.830
All seem surprised.

730
00:27:13.550 --> 00:27:16.850
Don César de Bezan, we have appointed you

731
00:27:16.850 --> 00:27:18.830
governor of Valencia.

732
00:27:19.430 --> 00:27:21.650
The government of Granada is also vacant,

733
