734
00:27:22.410 --> 00:27:25.010
Why rather Granada than Valencia?

735
00:27:25.690 --> 00:27:27.970
Granada is twice the distance from Madrid.

736
00:27:28.410 --> 00:27:29.970
Points to Maritana.

737
00:27:30.330 --> 00:27:31.890
And that doubles the obligation.

738
00:27:32.490 --> 00:27:35.110
And besides, there I've no creditors.

739
00:27:35.670 --> 00:27:36.890
King smiles.

740
00:27:37.470 --> 00:27:40.490
Be it as you wish, we appoint our

741
00:27:40.490 --> 00:27:44.270
faithful subject, Don César de Bezan,

742
00:27:44.750 --> 00:27:46.550
governor of Granada.

743
00:27:48.710 --> 00:27:49.510
Finale.

744
00:27:50.570 --> 00:27:52.170
Long live the king!

745
00:27:52.570 --> 00:27:54.330
Long live the king!

746
00:27:54.830 --> 00:27:56.550
Long live the king!

747
00:27:57.330 --> 00:28:00.110
Whoever repairs our love with love again,

748
00:28:00.510 --> 00:28:03.110
Let peace be joined to length of days.

749
00:28:03.630 --> 00:28:06.030
Let peace be joined to bless his happy

750
00:28:06.030 --> 00:28:06.670
